<html>

<head>
    <title>The Blockchain University</title>
</head>

<body>
<div style="font-family: Helvetica,sans-serif; padding: 9%; background-color: #ffffff; color: #333333; font-size: 17px;">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div style="vertical-align: middle; ">
        <img src="https://theblockchainu.com/assets/images/bu_logo.png" width="auto" height="35px" >  <span style="position: relative; top: -14px; color: #ff5b5f"></span>
    </div>
    <!-- Title -->
    <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 30px; margin-top: 40px;">
        Congrats on completing your <%= type %>!
    </div>
    <!-- Body -->
    <div>
        <div style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 25px;">
            Hey there,
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 20px; line-height: 24px">
            We hope what you've learned was both helpful and exciting.
            <br><br>
            We're also hoping you'll be inspired to go forward and share what you've learned with others.
            <br><br>
            <div style="display: inline-block; width: 30%;">
                <img src="https://theblockchainu.com:3000<%= collectionImage %>" alt="Cover Image" style="width: 100%;">
            </div>
            <div style="display: inline-block; width: 65%; padding-left: 20px; vertical-align: top;">
                <b><%= collectionTitle %></b>
                <br>
                <%= collectionStartDate %> - <%= collectionEndDate %>
                <br><br>
                <b><%= academicGyan %> Gyan</b> for academics.
                <br>
                <b><%= nonAcademicGyan %> Gyan</b> for commitment / engagement.
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <br><br>Below is a review of what you learned in this past <%= type %> so you can refresh anything that might have gone fuzzy in your memory - and it's here as a handy reference if you ever need it.
            <br><br>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    You spent over <b><%= viewTime %> hours</b> on this <b><%= days %> day</b> <%= type%>.<br><br>
                </li>
                <li>
                    You covered <b><%= contentCount %> activities</b> which included <b><%= contentSplit %>.</b><br><br>
                </li>
                <li>
                    During this period <b><%= totalCommentCount %> discussion</b> threads were started of which you were active in <%= personalCommentCount %>.
                    <br><br>
                </li>
                <li>
                    This <%= type %> covered <b><%= topics %> topics</b>.
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 21px; margin-top: 40px; line-height: 24px; background-color: #ff5b5f; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 4px;">
            <a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://theblockchainu.com/console/dashboard">View Learning Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Signature -->
    <div style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 30px; line-height: 24px;">
        Cheers,
        <br>
        The Blockchain U Team
    </div>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <hr style="margin-top: 40px; background-color: #dbdbdb;">
    <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #bbbbbb; margin-top: 30px; font-weight: 300">
        Sent with <span style="font-size: 11px;">&hearts;</span> from The Blockchain U
        <br><br>
        Peerbuds, Inc., 4580 Automall Pkwy, Fremont, CA 94538
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>